data.description: Great 3 bed plus loft town home in Maple Grove! Rentals allowed! Close to parks, trails, walking paths, and Arbor or Cedar Island Lakes and Play Field! Over $20,000 in updates since seller purchased in 2005! Updated kitchen with granite counters, natural travertine stone backsplash with mosaic glass accent, and 6???x6' pantry! Vaulted living room with durable Italian porcelain floor tile and updated light fixtures! The loft overlooks the living room, perfect for an office, den, or play area!  Expansive lower level third bedroom with porcelain tile floors and a walk-in closet along with a roughed-in bathroom! New carpet and paint! Professionally cleaned! Low association dues only $175/mo!
